snippet.textDisplay: One reference nobody seemed to catch:  The name Cherokee Jack comes from a character in the very B movie "Red Zone Cuba" (1966) that was riffed by Mystery Science Theater 3000. One of Coleman Francis's 3 movies done on that show in its original era in the '90s. Sly reference, with Michael Scott (or, more likely, the Office itself) acknowledging Threat Level Midnight as a cheesy "movie".  TLM even having a similar naming scheme to RZC!
